description: Officers clear a rare building still housing anarchists after decades of gentrification in the city.
title: Berlin Liebig 34 squat: German police evict dozens
title_page: Berlin Liebig 34 squat: German police evict dozens - BBC News
maintext: A lawyer for the squatters told AFP news agency: "It goes against human rights to throw people out on to the street in the middle of a pandemic, when they cannot pay their rents."
